            "type": "stat_block_section"
          },
          "effect": "Two crew members each perform a 3-action activity on their turn to release a massive buildup of steam around the vehicle, dealing 11d6 fire damage to each creature in a 10-foot emanation (DC 35 basic Reflex save). The release mechanism stops working if the vehicle is broken.",
